1. how to use docker to start the environment
docker run -it -v $(pwd):/home/packt/ml4t -p 8888:8888 -e QUANDL_API_KEY=<your API key> --name ml4t appliedai/packt:latest bash

2. how to close ml4t
sudo docker rm ml4t

3. how to study jupther
jupyter notebook --ip 0.0.0.0 --no-browser --allow-root
jupyter lab --ip 0.0.0.0 --no-browser --allow-root

4. which env to use
Part(s)	  Chapters	envs	
1, 2 & 3	2-16	    ml4t
4	        17-22	    ml4t_dl
